      <!-- VALUES -->
      <section class="values" id="values">
        <div class="container">
          <p class="section-label reveal"><i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i> &nbsp;What we stand for</p>
          <h2 class="section-title reveal">Built on principles<br /><em>parents care about.</em></h2>
          <p class="section-sub reveal">We believe in curiosity, wonder, and the magic of learning something
            new—together.
            We're building apps that will create meaningful experiences to bring families closer while exploring the
            natural
            world. From the sounds of the forest to the secrets of the animal kingdom, our experiences
            help kids explore nature, science, and the outdoors through imaginative play. Every interaction is crafted
            to
            spark curiosity and create lasting memories.</p>
          <div class="values-grid">
            <div class="value-card reveal">
              <div class="value-card-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-spa"></i></div>
              <h4>Calm by design</h4>
              <p>No flashing lights, no urgency loops, no addictive mechanics. Just gentle, peaceful play.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card reveal d1">
              <div class="value-card-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i></div>
              <h4>Safe & offline</h4>
              <p>Truly offline. No accounts, no data collection, no ads. Just a private, independent space to explore
                anywhere.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card reveal d2">
              <div class="value-card-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-graduation-cap"></i></div>
              <h4>Genuinely educational</h4>
              <p>Inspired by Montessori: discovery over instruction, curiosity over competition.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card reveal">
              <div class="value-card-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-palette"></i></div>
              <h4>Beautiful craft</h4>
              <p>Every detail is thoughtfully curated. Kids and parents deserve beautiful spaces to explore.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card reveal d1">
              <div class="value-card-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i></div>
              <h4>Shared wonder</h4>
              <p>Our apps are built for quality time. They are designed for side-by-side discovery, sparking the kind of
                curiosity that families enjoy together.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card reveal d2">
              <div class="value-card-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-infinity"></i></div>
              <h4>No subscriptions</h4>
              <p>Start your journey for free. If you love it, a single purchase unlocks a world of wonder forever.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="simple-gallery reveal" style="margin-top: 3.5rem;">
            <img src="images/gallery/thumbs/01.webp" class="landscape" loading="lazy"
              alt="A parent and child exploring nature together with Kidamame Discovery app" />
          </div>

        </div>
